title: A Peloton App Exclusive | The Elvis Remixes
author: Peloton
description:
There's always new music and new ways to work out on the Peloton App. And for a limited time, you can try the app free for 2 months, for new app trials only. Run, flow and get stronger to music made just for your workout—featuring Peloton-exclusive remixes by Big Boi, Chromeo and Dillon Francis. 

A Peloton App Exclusive | The Elvis Remixes

Download the app to move and groove to these tracks now.
